3. **Select Medians**: The optimal strategy involves selecting the medians from the sorted array in a specific pattern. Specifically, the medians are chosen from the positions starting from the second largest element (index `n-2`), then skipping the next element (to use it as the largest element in the triplet), and selecting the element two positions back from the previous median. This pattern is repeated k times to gather all medians.
